Package: RegCalReliab
Type: Package
Title: Regression Calibration Using Reliability Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Bowen", "Liu", email = "bowenliu@hsph.harvard.edu", 
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")),
    person("Yu", "Lu", role = "aut"),
    person("Molin", "Wang", role = "aut")
  )
Maintainer: Bowen Liu <bowenliu@hsph.harvard.edu>
Description: Implements regression calibration methods for correcting 
    measurement error in regression models using external or internal 
    reliability studies. Methods are described in Carroll, Ruppert, 
    Stefanski, and Crainiceanu (2006) "Measurement Error in Nonlinear 
    Models: A Modern Perspective" <doi:10.1201/9781420010138>.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
